## Supported controllers

### Hitachi HD44780

The hd44780 driver supports up to 4 rows of 20 characters. 

#### Enable check of busy state

Defining `HD44780_BUSYCHECK` as `1` will make the hd44780 driver check the
busy flag after each operation, rather than using a time-based approach. 

    HD44780_BUSYCHECK=[1|0]


